<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/style.css">
  
  

  <title>Kill Bill Fanpage</title>
</head>

<body>
  <script type="application/javascript" src="/script.js" defer></script>


  <section class="hero">
    <nav class="nav">
      <ul>
        <li>Home</li>
        <li>Code</li>
        <li>Prototype</li>

      </ul>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="bg">KILL BILL</h1>
    <div class="dir">
      <h4>WRITTEN AND DIRECTED BY</h4>
      <h4 class="q"> QUNENTIN TARANTINO</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="bar">


    </div>

    <div class="plot">An assassin is shot by her ruthless employer, Bill, and other members of</br>
       their assassination circle
      but she lives to plot her vengeance.</div>

    <div class="links">
      <div class="imdb" ></div>
      <div class="rt"></div>
      <div class="yt"></div>

    </div>

    <div class="img">
      <image src="/images/bride.png" height="600">

    </div>

  </section>
  
  <section class="review">
    <div class="bar">
      <h3>WRITE YOUR EMOTIONAL REVIEW</h3>
    </div>
    <p>
      What do you think about this movie?  We will analyze your tone, and colour code it.
    </p>

    <div class="input">
    <form action="/submit-form" method="GET">
      <label>
        Name:
        <input type="text" name="string1" maxlength="50" />
      </label>
      <label>
        Rating:
        <input type="number" name="number1" min="0" max="10" step="0.1" />
      </label>
      <br>
      <label>
        Review:</br>
        <textarea name="string2" rows="10" cols="50" maxlength="600"></textarea>
      </label> </br>
      <button class="submit" type="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>

    </div>
    
    <h3 class="rev">REVIEWS</h3>
    
    <div class="boxes">
      <% for (let i = data.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) { %>
        <div>
          <h4 class="name"><%= data[i].name %></h4>
          <p class="matter"><%= data[i].review %></p> 
          <h4 class="rating">Rating: <%= data[i].rating %></h4>
        </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>
    
    
  </section>
  
  <div class="bar3">  <h3>DID YOU KNOW?</h3> </div>

  <section class="facts">
   
    <div class="cube">
      <div class="side front"><h4>The Bride's yellow outfit was inspired by the outfit worn by Bruce Lee in his final film, Game of Death (1978).<h4></div>
      <div class="side back"><h4>Despite being bleeped out in the film, the name of The Bride is revealed on her plane tickets to Okinawa and Tokyo.</h4></div>
      <div class="side left"><h4>The members of the Deadly Viper Assassination Squad are all named after snakes. Bill drives a De Tomaso Mangusta. "Mangusta" is Italian for "Mongoose". </h4></div>
      <div class="side right"><h4>The name the sword maker, Hattori Hanzo, is also the name of a samurai who was a warrior for the shogun, Oda Nobunaga, in the year of 1570.</h4></div>
    </div>


  </section>


  <section class="trivia">
    <div class="bar4">
 
    <h3>  THE KILL BILL TRIVIA! </h3>
    
    
    </div>

    <div id="question-container" class="hide">
    <div id="question">Question</div>
  
    <div id="answer-buttons" class="button-grid" >
      <button class="button">Answer 1</button>
      <button class="button">Answer 2</button>
      <button class="button">Answer 3</button>
      <button class="button">Answer 4</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

    <div class="controls">
    <button id="start" class="start-btn btn btn">Start</button>
    <button id="next" class="next-btn btn hide">Next</button>
  </section>
<footer>
  Created By Bikku BS
</footer>
  
</body>

</html>